item.description: About Me I am a Junior at The University of Texas at Austin pursuing a BSA in Biology and a minor in communication studies. I have participated in Freshmen Research Initiative for two years, working on an independent project to select for an aptamer in hopes to relieve ALS. In addition, I am a marketing intern for PrideBites in Austin. My skills include proffieciency in Microsoft Office suites and R studio.
